text: Suputtra Beartong (born 31 August 1994) is a Thai female sepak takraw player. She represented Thailand at the 2018 Asian Games and was part of the Thai women's squad which clinched gold in the regu event. == References == Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Thai sportswomen Category:Sepak takraw players at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Medalists at the 2018 Asian Games Category:Asian Games gold medalists for Thailand Category:Asian Games medalists in sepak takraw Category:People from Pathum Thani Province Category:Sepak takraw players
